OL,3,CCalls for domestic abuse related
OL,4,Csuicides to be considered homicide
OL,6,FFamilies of people who have taken
OL,7,Ftheir own lives after domestic
OL,8,Fviolence are calling for abusers to
OL,9,Fface prosecution over their deaths.
OL,11,FAt a meeting in Westminster on
OL,12,FTuesday, bereaved families and MPs
OL,13,Fsaid suicide should be considered
OL,14,Fhomicide in cases where loved ones
OL,15,Fhave been driven to end their lives.
