OL,3,CCalls for domestic abuse related
OL,4,Csuicides to be considered homicide
OL,6,FSpeaking at the meeting, abuse
OL,7,Fsurvivor Saskia Lightburn-Ritchie and
OL,8,Fnow head of a charity, said: "Suicide
OL,9,Fis homicide when it's the final
OL,10,Fchapter of a story of abuse, and until
OL,11,Fwe recognise that and we hold abusers
OL,12,Faccountable, until we say their names
OL,13,Fout loud, we're failing every single
OL,14,Fvictim and every family that goes
OL,15,Fthrough this experience."
OL,17,FPhyllis Daly, the mother ofJessica
OL,18,FLaverack, who died in Beverley, East
OL,19,FYorkshire, in 2018, said: "The
OL,20,Fsystem's failed us as families."
