OL,3,CCalls for domestic abuse related
OL,4,Csuicides to be considered homicide
OL,6,FAccording to the charity Refuge, an
OL,7,Festimated three domestic abuse victims
OL,8,Fdie by suicide each week. Suicide
OL,9,Frates are now higher than homicide
OL,10,Ffigures.
OL,12,FFigures released by the Domestic
OL,13,FHomicide Project show that there were
OL,14,F1,012 domestic abuse-related deaths in
OL,15,FEngland and Wales between 2020 and
OL,16,F2024, of which 354 were suspected
OL,17,Fsuicides and 332 homicides.
