OL,3,CCalls for domestic abuse related
OL,4,Csuicides to be considered homicide
OL,6,FThe Suicide is Homicide campaign,
OL,7,Flaunched by women's group Project
OL,8,FResist alongside bereaved families
OL,9,Ffrom across the UK, is calling for
OL,10,Freform of the justice system.
OL,12,FThey want police to consider any
OL,13,Fsuicide following domestic abuse as a
OL,14,Fpotential homicide.
