OL,3,CCalls for domestic abuse related
OL,4,Csuicides to be considered homicide
OL,6,FIn a statement directors of Project
OL,7,FResist, Pragna Patel and Rosie Lewis,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Too many families who have lost
OL,9,Floved ones to suicides linked to
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse are being grievously
OL,11,Ffailed by a profoundly broken justice
OL,12,Fsystem.
OL,14,F"At the crux of the issue lies not a
OL,15,Fdeficiency of laws or an absence of
OL,16,Fawareness regarding domestic abuse and
OL,17,Fcoercive control, but rather a
OL,18,Fshocking and systemic failure of
OL,19,Fimplementation and accountability at
OL,20,Fevery level."
